Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:43.21,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We're all imperfect
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:52.60,OP-jp-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}光って見えない 未来の自分を創れるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:46.46,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't see it well in the light,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:52.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,350)}but if we can change our future selves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:59.54,OP-jp-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}目覚めるまま走れ 蜃気楼を追い越して
